author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Stud wall planing tips…I set the depth to 1/16 inch on this Makita planer. It only took a few passes to get the stud flat. This tool is great for proud studs and old doors that need fine tuning. Many thanks to @MakitaToolsUSA  for sending the planer and making projects like this a lot more fun 🔥#makitaadvantage #bathroomremodel #framing #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
